                        <interp inst="t18451215-name-398" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES WOOD</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 233.) I produce the certificate of the prisoner Jones's former conviction at Clerkenwell—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 25th Feb., 1845, and confined three months</hi>)—he is the person—he has been summarily convicted since.</p>
